<h2 id="_setting_up_a_user_account">1. Setting up a user account</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Your plentymarkets system will be connected to the IT-Recht Kanzlei via the SOAP interface, i.e. you require the SOAP module. In order for it to have access, this service requires its own user account with access rights to the API in your system.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a new user:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Accounts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>New</strong>.<br>
→ The editing window <strong>Create new user</strong> will appear.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the <strong>user name</strong>, the <strong>real name</strong> and the <strong>password</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Repeat the password.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the user’s email address. This will allow the user to receive messages from the system.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the user class <strong>API</strong> or <strong>Variable</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following calls must be activated for the user:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>GetServerTime</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>GetPlentyMarketsVersion</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>GetMultiShops</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>GetTermsAndCancellation</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>SetTermsAndCancellation</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>GetLegalInformation</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>SetLegalInformation</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For further information, refer to the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/setting-up-clients/extras/it-recht-kanzlei">Introduction to the SOAP API</a> page of the manual.</p>
</div>
</div>
