<h2 id="_automatically_transferring_legal_texts">2. Automatically transferring legal texts</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For IT-Recht Kanzlei to automatically transfer legal texts, set up a data interface in your IT-Recht Kanzlei account. The IT-Recht Kanzlei needs to have the following information from you in order to connect to your system:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Login details, user name and password</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>URL for the SOAP API WSDL<br>
This URL can be found in the <strong>Setup » Settings » API » Data</strong> menu under <a href="/en/basics/data-exchange/api-data">SOAP WSDL</a>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
